Riki -- High-DPS, starting stats 2 int, 10 agi, 3 str, base speed 280, base damage 8, Stats Gain per level 0.10 int, 0.20 str, 0.40 agi
starting item Weak Dagger increase damage by 2 and give 5 attackspeed base attack time 1.30

LEVEL 20 TALENT

talent 1

5 armor 90 movement and 300 life

talent 2

12 damage 20 attackspeed and 300 cast range



PASSIVE F OR D Thief Soul
increase overall stats and give a positive and negative buff

BUFF riki will gain 3 life per agility point he also get 10% increase agility for a total of his intelligence and strenght
DEBUFF riki only gain 2 life per strenght and he take 50% more damage from pure,magical,physical also he can only use dagger weapons type
he also lose 35% of his max mana with 20 attack speed lost

talent level 25 upgrade Thief Soul
add a new modifier Deadly
if riki attack the same target 3 time in a row the next attack will deal 4% of the target current life as damage
this effect only deal 1% of boss current life



SPELL Q Dagger Strike -NOTE- all riki spell and passive will deal damage base on this total basic attack damage
deal damage and reducing the enemy damage and attack speed for a short duration and after dealing the damage, the dagger
will bounce up to 4 target doing less damage and also reducing damage but not attackspeed

Attack damage 120% 130% 140% 150% damage type physical
damage reduction 6% 10% 14% 18%
attack speed lost 10 15 20 25
bouncing dagger damage 60% 65% 70% 75%
bouncing dagger damage reduction 3% 5% 7% 9%
debuff duration 7 second
mana cost 90 plus 2% of max mana
cooldown 15

talent level 10 upgrade Dagger Strike
increase damage by 30% -Note- 50% of this goes to the  lesser damage bounce dagger
increase damage reduction by 12% -Note- 50% of this goes to the  lesser damage bounce dagger
reduce mana cost by 30
reduce cooldown by 5

add a new modifier Poison Dagger
after striking the enemy,they will get poison dealing 7 plus 8% of agility pure damage per second and disabling regeneration
for 4, also increase the damage they take by riki spell by 20%


SPELL W Blink Stab
jump behind the enemy stunning them and dealing damage, after the stun the target get silence.

Attack damage 110% 140% 170% 200% damage type physical
stun 0.40 0.45 0.50 0.55
stun increase by 0.01 per agility point
silence 1.30 1.40 1.50 1.60
silence increase by 0.02 per agility point
mana cost 150 plus 1% of max mana
cooldown 28 26 24 22

talent level 10 upgrade Blink Stab
increase damage by 50%
increase stun by 0.15
increase silence by 0.40
reduce mana cost by 80

add a new modifier Stab Feast
after blinking on the target riki gets 25% increase damage and 20% of his damage become pure for 4 second, if any
enemy die by blink stab riki will get heal for 35% of is max life and increase the next blink stab damage by 20% this can chain
up to 100% more damage, this bonus is lost if the target dont die by blink stab


SPELL E Smoke Grenade
Throw a smoke at the target location dealing small amount of damage and causing enemy to miss and get slow
also increase ally magic resist

Attack damage 25% 35% 45% 55% damage type magical
miss chance 4% 8% 12% 16%
movementspeed slow 15%
magic resist bonus 4% 7% 10% 13%
radius 250
radius increase by 2 per agility point
the smoke last 5 6 7 8 second
the smoke duration increase by 0.02 per agility point
mana cost 100 130 160 190 plus 4% of max mana
cooldown 22 21 20 19

talent level 15 upgrade Smoke Grenade
increase miss chance by 14%
increase slow by 15%
increase magic resist by 7%
increase radius by 150

add a new modifier Toxic Smoke
deal 15% of riki attack damage as magic per second and the enemy got 15% chance to be stun for 0.60 second every
tick of damage also give allys and riki 15 flat base damage while inside of it


PASSIVE D OR F BackStab -NOTE- this affect only work behind that mean if riki attack from the front once the target lose all stack
increase riki agility, riki attack will do 100% crit damage behind the target and lowering the armor of the target as well
if the target get 6 stack of Stab he will take increase damage

base agility bonus 5 7 9 11
damage multiplier behind the target 110% 120% 130% 140%
armor lost per stack 1
damage increase 9% 11% 13% 15%
damage increase duration 3 second
armor lost duration 2 second
-NOTE- has no cooldown to regive the stack again meaning that with alot of attack speed the increase damage can stay for infinit time

talent level 15 upgrade BackStab
increase damage multiplier by 20%
increase damage taken by 15%
increase agility bonus by 9

add a new modifier DeepStab
riki got 30% chance to deal 250% of the normal damage behind and giving 3 stack instead of 1, riki also
get 15% lifesteal on proc and he also give 40% of his agility to near ally 900 radius


ULTMATE R Assasin Parry PASSIVE
riki can parry any melee attack dealing bonus damage to them and reducing damage he take as well, riki will gain
a stack of Parry increasing armor by 2 up to a max of 10, after 5 stack next parry will do max life damage also
increase riki damage

bonus damage 10% 15% 20%
Attack damage to parry 200% 300% 400% damage type pure
parry chance 11% 13% 15%
damage reduction upon parrying 10% 20% 30%
max stack parry damage 5% 10% 15% of max life as damage of the enemy
parry stack duration 10 second
armor per stack 2

talent level 25 upgrade Assasin Parry
increase bonus damage by 15%
increase attack damage by 40%
increase parry chance by 1%
increase the damage of max life by 10%
increase the duration of stack by 5

add a new modifier Death Strike
riki basic attack will alway deal 10% pure damage and 30% of the damage done by parry will be life bonus for riki that last 11 second
refreshing by 2 second upon parrying again, riki also gain 0.50 more attack speed from agility and 2 movement speed as well and
increasing is speed limit to 750



